{
  "id": "699bc5301e6e9bfc31456b6f",
  "title": "Cosenseをチャットとして使っている人",
  "created": 1771816243,
  "updated": 1771818702,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "699bc5301e6e9bfc31456b6f",
      "text": "Cosenseをチャットとして使っている人",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816243,
      "updated": 1771816258
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc542000000000009dcca",
      "text": "　実務やある程度大きなコミュニティで[Cosense]をチャットとして使っている人がいたら話を聞きたい",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816258,
      "updated": 1771816311
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc577000000000009dccc",
      "text": "　困りそうなこと",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816311,
      "updated": 1771816394
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc5c9000000000009dccd",
      "text": "　\t通知",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816394,
      "updated": 1771816396
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc5d6000000000009dcce",
      "text": "　\t既読管理",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816406,
      "updated": 1771816409
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc5d9000000000009dccf",
      "text": "　\tDMができない",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816409,
      "updated": 1771816415
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc5de000000000009dcd0",
      "text": "　\tモバイルのUXが弱い",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816415,
      "updated": 1771816429
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc65b00000000008bc715",
      "text": "　\t公式のAPIがないので外部連携が弱い",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816540,
      "updated": 1771816553
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc66800000000008bc716",
      "text": "　\tページが増えすぎる",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816553,
      "updated": 1771816563
    },
    {
      "id": "699bcec3000000000071e092",
      "text": "　\t他人の書いたことが消せてしまう",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771818691,
      "updated": 1771818702
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc542000000000009dccb",
